    Salem Steamer serves the McLean and Washington, DC metropolitan area and is built on a simple principle: every property and every client deserves the highest standard of care. Using the latest restoration technology, we restore 100% of your environment, leaving zero visible traces we were ever there.

    What Sets Us Apart

    White-Glove Service for Every Client

    Our teams are vetted, uniformed, and professional. We communicate clearly, protect your privacy, and ensure a seamless experienceno matter the size of your project.

    Technical Expertise for Any Finish

    We employ advanced, industry-leading techniques for soot, odor, and mold remediation that are safe for any surfacefrom antique hardwood to modern building materials.

    A Public Adjuster, Paid by Us

    For clients navigating insurance claims, we provide a public adjusterat our costwho will negotiate on your behalf for the fullest and fairest settlement possible.

    Third-Party Certified Lab Report

    We engage an independent, third-party certified laboratory to scientifically analyze post-remediation samples and validate that your indoor air quality meets stringent health standards.

    As Discreet as You Want Us to Be

    Our discretion premium ensures your home's history remains private. Options include unmarked vehicles, sealed records, paperless transactions, NDAs, and code names.
